page_number":588,"text_uthmani":"إِذَا تُتۡلَىٰ عَلَيۡهِ ءَايَٰتُنَا قَالَ أَسَٰطِيرُ ٱلۡأَوَّلِينَ ١٣","text_indopak":"اِذَا تُتۡلٰى عَلَيۡهِ اٰيٰتُنَا قَالَ اَسَاطِيۡرُ الۡاَوَّلِيۡنَؕ‏","text_uthmani_tajweed":"إِذَا تُتْلَىٰ عَلَيْهِ ءَايَ<tajweed class=madda_normal>ـٰ</tajweed>تُنَا قَالَ أَسَ<tajweed class=madda_normal>ـٰ</tajweed>طِيرُ <tajweed class=ham_wasl>ٱ</tajweed>لْأَوَّل<tajweed class=madda_permissible>ِي</tajweed>نَ <span class=end>١٣</span>"},{"id":5862,"verse_key":"83:14","chapter_id":83,"verse_number":14,"juz_number":30,"hizb_number":59,"rub_el_hizb_number":235,"page_number":588,"text_uthmani":"كـَلَّاۖ بَلۡۜ رَانَ عَلَىٰ قُلُوبِهِم مَّا كَانُواْ يَكۡسِبُونَ ١٤","text_indopak":"كَلَّا​ بَلۡ رَانَ عَلٰى قُلُوۡبِهِمۡ مَّا كَانُوۡا يَكۡسِبُوۡنَ‏","text_uthmani_tajweed":"كَلَّا‌ۖ بَلْۜ رَانَ عَلَىٰ قُلُوبِه<tajweed class=idgham_shafawi>ِم م</tajweed>َّا كَانُو<tajweed class=slnt>اْ</tajweed> يَكْسِب<tajweed class=madda_permissible>ُو</tajweed>نَ <span class=end>١٤</span>"},{"id":5863,"verse_key":"83:15","chapter_id":83,"verse_number":15,"juz_number":30,"hizb_number":59,"rub_el_hizb_number":235,"page_number":588,"text_uthmani":"كـَلَّآ إِنَّهُمۡ عَن رَّبِّهِمۡ يَوۡمَئِذٖ لَّمَحۡجُوبُونَ ١٥","text_indopak":"كَلَّاۤ اِنَّهُمۡ عَنۡ رَّبِّهِمۡ يَوۡمَٮِٕذٍ لَّمَحۡجُوۡبُوۡنَ​ؕ‏","text_uthmani_tajweed":"كَلّ<tajweed class=madda_obligatory>َآ</tajweed> إِ<tajweed class=ghunnah>نّ</tajweed>َهُمْ ع<tajweed class=idgham_wo_ghunnah>َن ر</tajweed>َّبِّهِمْ يَوْمَئِ<tajweed class=idgham_wo_ghunnah>ذٍ ل</tajweed>َّمَحْجُوب<tajweed class=madda_permissible>ُو</tajweed>نَ <span class=end>١٥</span>"},{"id":5864,"verse_key":"83:16","chapter_id":83,"verse_number":16,"juz_number":30,"hizb_number":59,"rub_el_hizb_number":235,"page_number":588,"text_uthmani":"ثُمَّ إِنَّهُمۡ لَصَالُواْ ٱلۡجَحِيمِ ١٦","text_indopak":"ثُمَّ اِنَّهُمۡ لَصَالُوا الۡجَحِيۡمِؕ‏","text_uthmani_tajweed":"ثُ<tajweed class=ghunnah>مّ</tajweed>َ إِ<tajweed class=ghunnah>نّ</tajweed>َهُمْ لَصَالُو<tajwe